  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "This model has been applied in clinical research settings to evaluate hemolysis risk for centrifugal blood pump configurations under ventricular assist device operating conditions. The CFD hemolysis prediction framework targets the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry. Credibility assessment covers 13 factors at Model Risk Level 5; seven factors were formally assessed and six were flagged as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across inlet flow rate and rotational speed parameters. All assessed credibility factors achieved required levels under the Minimal profile declaration. The assessment team concludes that the model is suitable for the intended research application. No structured Context of Use object is provided under this profile submission; the intended-use scope is conveyed through narrative description only.",
