      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Dimensional and non-dimensional equivalency between simulation inputs and experimental conditions must be formally documented.",
      "rationale": "Reynolds number and flow coefficient matching between simulation and experiment is asserted but not formally documented through a structured equivalency analysis. This factor is flagged as an epistemic gap pending formal documentation."
    }
