    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Under the Minimal profile declaration, the seven assessed credibility factors all achieved required levels. The six not-assessed factors are acknowledged as epistemic gaps at MRL 5 and are documented for future assessment cycles. The assessment team judges the model fit for purpose for the clinical research application described in the narrative, with the understanding that the not-assessed factors represent limitations to be addressed before any regulatory submission. The Minimal profile is appropriate for the current research-use context.",
